Package: HARMONI
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical Association Resolution via Multivariate Orthogonalized Non-Null Inference
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Dipta", family = "Dutta", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dipta.dutta@nih.gov")
Description: Joint Bayesian modeling of pooled and subtype-specific PWAS
    or TWAS association statistics. HARMONI decomposes the observed
    association pattern into shared and heterogeneity contrasts, estimates
    posterior support for null, shared, and heterogeneous configurations,
    and returns Bayesian false discovery summaries together with posterior
    effect estimates.
